0th.270: Firefighters from the Monroe Fire Protection District and Washington Township Fire in Morgan County extinguish a fire that began when a truck carrying paint exploded, and then caught two barns on fire in the 4500 block of East Hacker Creek Road, on July 20, 2022 near Martinsville, Indiana. One person had minor burns from the fire.
